    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Nearly all the &quot;fun&quot; of Smalltalk is that you can dynamically interact with the objects that you create. Why not now try some experiments on your own? Ask the </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Playground</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> objects to perform some operations and then query their states. Perhaps you&apos;ll want to add some new shapes. </text></para>
